# Assets Other Financial Assets Reverse Repurchase Agreements Principal Amount

## identifier
de15160

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of the principal amount of cash lent (post haircut) on the initial leg of a reverse repo, the buyer of the asset in a repo is referred to as conducting a reverse repo.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.OtherFinancialAssets.ReverseRepurchaseAgreementsPrincipal.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo7.02.27
- period=instant
